## Data Usage
1. This application scrapes holiday data from officeholidays.com for informational
purposes only. Users are responsible for verifying the accuracy of holiday information.

2. The application stores minimal data locally on the user's device to prevent
duplicate notifications. No personal data is collected or transmitted.

